/*
 * V7 - UNIFIED FLOW (COMPLETE)
 * 
 * Key features:
 * - Single box throughout (no separate cards or views)
 * - Same background (no theme transitions)
 * - Copy + Edit buttons always present (bottom center of box)
 * - Double-click pattern: first click highlights, second drills
 * 
 * States:
 * - INPUT: Type or chat with AI to build prompt
 *   - Sparkle button toggles AI chat mode
 *   - Can discuss prompt requirements with AI
 *   - Upload button active for reference files
 * 
 * - REVIEW: Single box with full prompt text
 *   - Copy button (with "Copied!" feedback)
 *   - Edit button (inline editing, not separate view)
 *   - Sparkle enters analysis
 * 
 * - ANALYSIS_OVERVIEW: Same box, sections become interactive
 *   - Sections separated with dividers
 *   - Click once â†’ highlights section
 *   - Click again (within 2s) â†’ drills into detail
 *   - Add/delete sections via pills below box
 *   - Revert button in header
 * 
 * - ANALYSIS_SECTION: Detail view for selected section
 *   - Quick actions (Expand/Condense) on highlighted elements
 *   - Main box clickable to highlight
 *   - Subsections clickable to highlight
 *   - Chat with sparkle button
 *   - Back returns to overview
 * 
 * Dynamic section generation:
 * - Only creates relevant sections based on input
 * - Core sections always included: Role & Context, Task & Objective
 * - Optional sections added based on keywords:
 *   - Process & Steps: if mentions "process", "step", "workflow", "how"
 *   - Rules & Constraints: if mentions "rule", "constraint", "must", "avoid"
 *   - Output Format: if mentions "output", "format", "provide"
 *   - Examples: if mentions "example", "sample", "like"
 * - Defaults to 3 sections minimum
 * - Max 6 sections total
 * 
 * Section management:
 * - Add button cycles through missing standard sections first
